original_title: 25th Asian Athletic Championships: Nadeesha Ramanayake wins gold medal in women’s 400m
original_body_lines: Nadeesha Ramanayake wins gold medal in women's 400m with a timing of 52.61 seconds at the 25th Asian Athletic Championships, which is being held currently in Bangkok, Thailand.
